# 🎨 Design Principles

### 1. Large Buttons

Many users may be older adults.

Buttons should be easy to tap.

---

### 2. Large Fonts

Health information must be easy to read.

---

### 3. White Background

Healthcare apps should feel clean.

---

### 4. Limited Colors

Use colors with meaning:

🟢 Normal

🟡 Borderline

🔴 Needs attention

Don't overuse colors.

---

### 5. Avoid Medical Jargon

Instead of:

> "Hypovitaminosis D"

Use:

> "Your Vitamin D is below the reference range shown on the report."

