# 💡 One Improvement I'd Recommend

I would add a **floating "Upload Report" button** on the Home screen.

Instead of making users search for the upload option, a prominent button at the bottom-right makes the app's primary action immediately obvious. Since uploading reports is the core purpose of your app, that action should always be easy to find.

